-- Sinopec Boosts Crude Oil Refining Capacity at Tahe Plant to 5 Million Tons
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-09-21T02:33:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/sinopec-boosts-crude-oil-refining-capacity-at-tahe-plant-to-5-million-tons.html

          
          
             China Petroleum & Chemical Corp.,
the nation’s biggest oil refiner, has raised its Tahe plant’s
processing capacity to 5 million metric tons a year, its parent
China Petrochemical Corp. said in a statement on its website
today.  
